---
description: Keep agent replies short and actionable
alwaysApply: true
---

# Concise responses

- Lead with the answer or decision in 1–2 sentences.
- Use short bullet lists for steps and checklists; avoid long prose.
- No repeating context the user already knows.
- Code citations only when they help navigation; skip large dumps.
- For deploy/test tasks: numbered steps, env vars, and URLs — nothing else unless asked.
